                <note rend="inline" type="source">612.119/2840</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Memorandum of a Conversation between the Secretary of State
                        and the Mexican Chargé</hi> (<hi rend="italic">Diego-Fernandez</hi>), <hi
                        rend="italic">April 15, 1920</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-head" calendar="gregorian"
                        type="conversation-or-meeting-date" when="1920-04-15">April 15, 1920</date>
                </dateline>
                <p>The Chargé d’Affaires of Mexico again called attention to the shipment of arms
                    across our frontier which might be consigned to or eventually reach the
                    rebellious element in Mexico.</p>
